
Viscrow Aria

Viscrow's AI Scribe Software

Dev Setup

Required Microservices

userService
deepgramProxy
inference
Environment Variables

Make sure you are running the other backend services first

VITE_AUTH_URL=<base url of the userService api>
VITE_TRANSCRIPTION_URL=<base url of the deepgramProxy api>
VITE_NOTES_URL=<base url of the inference api>
Installation

Make sure you have pnpm installed on your computer

PNPM installation instructions can be found here

To install dependencies, run pnpm install in the project folder
To run the app, run pnpm run dev in the project folder
